            "name": "Spear Frog",
            "type": "section",
            "text": "The spear frog is named for its toxin, which is traditionally used to envenom thrown projectiles like spears and daggers.<br/><br/><b><u><a aonid=\"5\" game-obj=\"Skills\" general=\"true\">Recall Knowledge - Animal</a></u> (<u><a aonid=\"10\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Nature</a></u>)</b>: DC 14",
